reviewText: This video is just an attempt to separate Beatle fans from their money. There is nothing new or revelatory  about this program. It is just a group of guys talking about the Beatles as if they had a connection to them or the filming of "Magical Mystery Tour". Save your time, save your money -  just leave this tripe alone.
Talking heads.  Miniscule clips in the background but what you see are more talking heads.
